} 这里是编译错误： $ cargo run Compiling ownership v0.1.0 (file:///projects/ownership)
error[E0502]: cannot borrow `s` as mutable because it is also borrowed as immutable --> src/main.rs:18:5 |
16 | let word = first_word(&s); | -- immutable borrow occurs here
17 | 18 | s.clear(); // error! | ^^^^^^^^^ mutable borrow occurs here
19 | 20 | println!("the first word is: {}", word); | ---- immutable borrow later used here For more information about this error, try `rustc --explain E0502`.
